FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Common questions about our Ethereum transaction analysis app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app provides real-time analysis of new transactions on the Ethereum blockchain. It monitors the network, decodes incoming transactions, and extracts valuable insights from the data.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: What kind of analysis is performed?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: The app analyzes transaction details like sender, recipient, value transferred, gas used, and smart contract interactions. It also identifies patterns, detects anomalies, and tracks activity from specific addresses of interest.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How quickly are new transactions analyzed?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Our system processes new blocks and transactions in real-time as they are mined, providing analysis within seconds after data becomes available on the Ethereum network.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I integrate the app with my own systems?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, we offer API access and webhook integrations so you can pipe the transaction analysis data directly into your own applications, dashboards, or alerting systems.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We have a free tier for basic usage and paid subscriptions that unlock higher transaction volumes, more advanced filtering, long-term data retention, and priority support.
